		<th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" height="25" width="100">&nbsp;Author</th><th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" width="85%">&nbsp;Thread: Amateur Trak Homework to be graded and corrected please</th>
	</tr><tr>
		<td class="PanelBody" nowrap="nowrap" valign="Top" width="150"><table border="0">
			<tr>
				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Wiladancer is not online. Last active: 8/25/2004 1:37:03 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Wiladancer">Wiladancer</a><br><a class="SmallText" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=137627" target="_new">Wiladancer's Homepage</a></td>
